 *
 *   - before

 *   - fun

 *   - after

 *
 *
 * @example
 * import Benchmark from 'promise-bench';
 * 
 * 
 * new Benchmark({
 *     name: 'timeout',
 *     fun() {
 *         return new Promise((resolve, reject) => {
 *             setTimeout(resolve, 100);
 *         });
 *     },
 * }).run().catch(console.error);
